Package fr.internetcartographier.model.geolocationservice

Class IPAddress

java.lang.Object
fr.internetcartographier.model.geolocationservice.IPAddress
public class IPAddress extends Object
The IPAddress class represents an IP address and provides utility methods for working with IP addresses.
